    12| *   - Accepts ONLY a valid `ivx_test_*` token via Authorization: Bearer.
    13| *   - On success: creates a test job, drives the worker once, returns the
    14| *     full transcript (job + logs).
    15| *   - Token is invalidated immediately on consumption.
    16| *
    17| * Token store is process-local (Map). With a 10-min TTL and single-use
    18| * semantics this is appropriate: a restart simply invalidates outstanding
    19| * tokens, which is the safe default for a test-only credential.
    20| *
    21| * The mint route NEVER returns or accepts scopes outside of
